The paper discusses the interaction between users and intelligent systems, which falls under the category of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). The focus is on user modeling and human-computer interaction (cs.HC), as well as machine learning (cs.LG) and information retrieval (cs.IR) techniques used to model user behavior. The paper also discusses the use of probabilistic programming (cs.SI) to implement the proposed model.
